{"tid":999204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一周吃5次燒烤！30歲男大便有血　就醫檢查…大腸癌末期","createTime":"2019-01-28T14:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T18:34:50.000Z","uid":212399,"like":146,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"db6d6baef69f57a1e7dc9a649879b1c6fff464a3","tid":999204,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T14:04:55.000Z","msg":"生活中心／綜合報導<br />\n大陸江蘇省南京市一名30歲男子熱愛吃燒烤，一周至少吃5天，有「燒烤王子」之稱。沒想到男子突然出現血便，就醫檢查後發現已經是大腸癌末期，連動手術的機會都沒有！<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/03/06/830446-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F03%2F06%2F830446-XXL.jpg&h=0af9c4b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼男子一周吃5次燒烤，結果罹患大腸癌。（圖／資料照）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/09/30/1076261-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F1076261-XXL.jpg&h=7b93bf83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n綜合陸媒報導，一名男子前年結婚後，非常喜歡吃燒烤，整個南京市的燒烤店幾乎都被他吃遍了，後來男子出現血便症狀，起初他以為是痔瘡沒有多想，直到症狀越來越嚴重才就醫，結果檢查後，發現自己罹患大腸癌末期。<br />\n醫師表示，從罹患大腸癌的案例來看，在沒有基因遺傳的人中，通常都有飲食不規律、愛吃宵夜、燒烤等特點。醫師提醒，50歲以上是大腸癌高危險族群，一旦出現腹痛、腹瀉、大便中有黏液膿血等情況時，應盡速就醫檢查，以免錯失治療良機。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/News.aspx?NewsID=491747\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D491747&d=lCA45G8Nzi7RNDaJePiRJ10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=9cfb18a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D491747&h=0cf4ee28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/News.aspx?NewsID=491747</a>"},{"pid":"b32ad984ea55cd81136bc572548135c0cf91da3e","tid":999204,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T14:05:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a3a52ef9790d23c60733ba732d48abc15194c0a","tid":999204,"uid":82532,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":